SubHeading1_summary = 'Effective project scheduling and management are essential for ensuring that an Android app is developed on time and within budget. By creating a well-defined timeline and assigning clear roles and responsibilities, app development companies can streamline the development process and maximize efficiency.'
SubHeading2 = 'Perform Value Engineering'
SubHeading2_summary = 'Value engineering is a key concept in app development that involves identifying and eliminating unnecessary features or functionalities that do not add value to the end product. By focusing on the core functionalities that matter most to users, app development companies can create apps that are more user-friendly and cost-effective.'
SubHeading3 = 'Safety Net & Build Wealth'
